can start a new life together."],[3820,3958,"You're nuts"],[3958,4079,"if you think I want a new life"],[4079,4149,"with you."],[4149,4408,"Your love can never compare to his."],[4441,4512,"Sarah..."],[4575,4721,"don't you see how much I love you?"],[4721,4763,"I've done"],[4763,4884,"so many terrible things"],[4884,4959,"for you."],[4959,5096,"Actually,"],[5096,5271,"I may be willing to"],[5271,5409,"hear your proposal."],[5467,5613,"If you do one"],[5613,5743,"tiny thing"],[5743,5826,"for me."],[5980,6072,"Kill Nicole."],[6089,6260,"Do it with this knife."],[6260,6335,"Make her suffer"],[6335,6435,"like she made me suffer"],[6435,6506,"watching Ethan"],[6506,6623,"choose her over me."],[6660,6802,"You're crazy..."],[6802,6873,"Wasn't the plan"],[6873,7011,"to get her out of this town?"],[7065,7290,"Sarah, I've already killed two Wilsons."],[7290,7365,"Okay, I've got enough"],[7365,7515,"blood on my hands as it is!"],[7557,7632,"They're talking about"],[7632,7791,"what happened to Ethan's parents."],[7791,7857,"They..."],[7857,7999,"they're the ones who killed them!"],[8350,8454,"Looks like someone heard something"],[8454,8575,"they weren't supposed to."]],"35":[[70,196,"What are you doing?"],[304,525,"Why did you kill Ethan's parents,"],[525,734,"and put this all on me?"],[796,971,"Those two old fools"],[971,1155,"actually chose you over me."],[1188,1322,"I'm the Miller heiress,"],[1322,1422,"I'm supposed to be"],[1422,1597,"his perfect match!"],[1618,1743,"You're nuts!"],[1830,1964,"You know too much,"],[1964,2081,"and people who know too much"],[2081,2185,"have to die."],[2243,2360,"It’s the perfect time."],[2431,2519,"Do it!"],[2519,2660,"Ethan will not let us get away"],[2660,2740,"with this."],[2740,2948,"I already have her resignation letter."],[2948,3140,"I'll just give Ethan some excuse."],[3345,3486,"Think about it."],[3524,3699,"She knows about the car crash."],[3699,3807,"She can tell everyone,"],[3807,3958,"and I'll be exposed."],[4045,4258,"Didn't you