ives."],[6147,6189,"Now."]],"42":[[566,704,"Sarah, what are you doing here?"],[970,1020,"You psycho!"],[1020,1141,"What did you do to my grandma?"],[1258,1423,"That old hag raised a little slut"],[1423,1575,"who seduces married men."],[1666,1812,"She got what she deserves."],[3133,3266,"On your knees, bitch!"],[3304,3337,"Oh!"],[3620,3733,"You've been hanging around"],[3733,3841,"the Wilsons, haven't you?"],[3841,3937,"Buttering up Lila"],[3937,4041,"just get to Ethan."],[4079,4212,"Ethan completely lost it"],[4212,4308,"when you got kidnapped."],[4308,4404,"But when the same thing happened"],[4404,4516,"to me, he didn't even blink."],[4570,4662,"You've been messing around"],[4662,4700,"with Henry."],[4700,4845,"You don't deserve Ethan!"],[4908,5137,"Who the hell do you think you are?"],[5187,5333,"Ethan and I are solid,"],[5333,5512,"so stop trying to wreck my family!"],[5512,5637,"So what if he got his memory back?"],[5637,5770,"He's never gonna be yours!"],[6229,6350,"He got his memory back?"],[6579,6708,"Even if he got his memory back,"],[6708,6862,"he'll never be yours."],[7041,7204,"If you want your blind old"],[7204,7304,"granny to stay alive,"],[7350,7579,"you better stay the hell out of our lives."],[7683,7804,"What did you do with my grandma?"],[7804,7920,"Where is she?"]],"43":[[0,62,"Grandma!"],[370,545,"Grandma, please wake up."],[604,666,"Wake up please."],[666,850,"Ms. Miller went easy on her,"],[850,1016,"just a couple of sleeping pills."],[1016,1183,"But if you don't back off,"],[1183,1351,"next time it won't be so gentle."],[1762,1883,"Let's not forget"],[1883,2037,"I still have Lila."],[2037,2241,"Stop messing with my family."],[2241,2355,"Do you really want Lila"],[2355,2533,"to grow up in a broken home?"],[2850,2964,"Fine, I will leave."],[3254,3441,"Grandma is all I have left,"],[3441,3654,"and Lila is such a sweetie,"],[3654,3766,"I can't let anything happen"],[3766,3933,"to the people that I care about."],[4287,4429,"Once grandma's out of the hospital,"],[4429,4575,"we're leaving the city for good."],[4620,4729,"I'll find another job"],[4729,4891,"and get her the surgery she needs."],[6350,6483,"Nicole, I remember everything now."],[6483,6625,"Please, don't go!"]],"44":[[70,150,"It's been seven years,"],[150,283,"and I can't lose you again."],[420,533,"I remember everything now."],[533,650,"I remember every moment."],[666,813,"I remember every part of you."],[919,1035,"Please, please, please..."],[1035,1186,"can we just pick up where we left off?"],[1254,1368,"I'm sorry that I hurt you,"],[1368,1479,"I'm sorry I forgot you."],[1479,1595,"But deep down Nicole,"],[1678,1850,"I always remembered you."],[1979,2042,"It's me."],[2068,2204,"Nicole, It's me, it's Ethan."],[2304,2452,"Hey, hey."],[2512,2604,"You love me."],[2627,2676,"Mr. Wilson..."],[2676,2786,"And I've always loved you."],[3066,3175,"Mr. Wilson."],[3175,3229,"Yeah?"],[3229,3375,"It's been seven years."],[3483,3562,"It's over."],[3620,3708,"What?"],[3783,3879,"It's over?"],[3941,4054,"We are in love Nicole."],[4187,4329,"We are deeply in love."],[4370,4466,"You can't pretend like that"],[4466,4566,"just didn't happen."],[4775,4983,"You are mad at me, right?"],[4983,5095,"That's why you're saying these things."],[5095,5225,"You're trying to hurt me."],[5225,5312,"No I'm not,"],[5312,5375,"I'm not."],[5795,5912,"I am moving on."],[6050,6141,"Whatever happened"],[6141,6287,"between us, it is in the past."],[6475,6629,"You need to let it go."],[6629,6808,"You need to let me go."],[6808,6954,"Let it go?"],[6954,7112,"Nicole, we had something real."],[7112,7233,"It can't be erased, even if I don't"],[7233,7325,"remember it."],[7491,7550,"You remember."],[7550,7645,"You were just holding the ring"],[7645,7770,"that I proposed to you with."],[7862,7962,"Ethan and I are from"],[7962,8158,"different worlds, I see that now."],[8158,8308,"I can't let myself fall for him again."],[8737,8850,"Even if my mind"],[8929,9037,"never remembered you,"],[9037,9133,"my heart always did."],[9204,9333,"You're always going to be a part of me."],[9333,9437,"Nicole, please, just give me"],[9437,9566,"a second chance."],[9566,9637,"Please!"]],"45":[[33,125,"The engagement ring"],[125,387,"that you got me I lost that"],[387,513,"years ago."],[808,1054,"This ring is a gift from my husband."],[1327,1465,"Your husband?"],[1545,1641,"Yes."],[1641,1775,"I don' believe you."],[1966,2062,"Mr. Wilson,"],[2200,2287,"I'm married."],[2491,2541,"Honey?"],[2675,2795,"I've been waiting outside."],[2987,3050,"Hey Ethan."],[3116,3304,"I... didn't expect to see you here."],[3516,3687,"You're marrying Liam?"],[3687,3895,"The guy that you tutored in college?"]],"46":[[154,254,"Mr. Wilson,"],[366,437,"whatever happened"],[437,564,"in the past is over."],[712,820,"I wish for you"],[958,1116,"so much happiness."],[1304,1412,"And I hope that you would wish"],[1412,1529,"the same for us."],[1529,1604,"No."],[1679,1875,"I can only be truly happy with you."],[2495,2599,"Goodbye, Ethan."],[4201,4318,"You okay?"],[4520,4637,"I'm okay."],[4725,4920,"Thank you for acting back there."],[5487,5576,"Take your time."],[6466,6654,"Goodbye, Ethan."],[7485,7602,"Ethan!"],[7602,7715,"Why did you leave the hospital"],[7715,7835,"so soon?"],[7835,8048,"You scared me and Lila half to death."],[8048,8195,"Sara, is Lila our daughter?"]],"47":[[313,521,"What kind of question is that?"],[521,662,"Oh my God! Get her out of here."],[862,999,"Wait! Ethan, what's going on?"],[1075,1200,"Where is he taking me?"],[1200,1333,"To take a DNA test."],[1483,1579,"For what?"],[1579,1761,"Lila is our daughter!"],[1761,1975,"She's our... oh... off me!"],[2045,2208,"Before the accident,"],[2208,2373,"I never even touched Sarah."],[2441,2537,"How could we possibly"],[2537,2637,"have a child?"],[2883,2975,"Good thing the hospital"],[2975,3162,"let me work to pay off grandma's bills."],[3362,3520,"Did you hear about the Wilsons?"],[3554,3729,"Mr. Wilson's getting DNA tests"],[3742,3875,"for Ms. Miller and the girl."],[3875,4037,"He thinks the kid's not hers."],[4037,4133,"Yeah, I saw her."],[4133,4241,"She looks pretty sick."],[4241,4383,"Hooked up to an IV."],[4383,4541,"Malnutrition."],[4604,4750,"Apparently, she stopped eating"],[4750,4937,"when the nanny left last week."],[4937,5029,"Well, if that woman,"],[5029,5150,"Sarah really is her mother,"],[5150,5308,"she sure doesn't act like it."],[5362,5437,"What?"],[5483,5660,"Lila looks just like Ethan."],[5720,5937,"If my baby had lived,"],[5937,6037,"would she have looked like"],[6037,6241,"Ethan or me?"],[6294,6516,"Could she have, taken my baby?"],[6779,6970,"Could Lila be my daughter?"],[7129,7240,"I have to find out!"]],"48":[[954,1104,"Poor Lila..."],[1104,1316,"She looks so weak."],[1316,1429,"Must be hard having no one here"],[1429,1612,"to take care of her."],[2416,2475,"Oh, no."],[2516,2562,"Ethan is here,"],[2562,2654,"I can't let him see me."],[2737,2850,"How's Lila doing?"],[2872,3041,"Oh! Mr. Wilson."],[3137,3233,"Lila's fever has started"],[3233,3316,"to come down."],[3362,3442,"Mr. Wilson,"],[3501,3637,"the DNA test results are in."],[4208,4412,"Sarah and Lila are..."]],"49":[[652,725,"Sarah and Lila"],[725,862,"are perfect genetic match."],[975,1170,"Lila is my biological daughter."],[1212,1412,"So Lila is not my baby."],[1412,1629,"She's Sarah's and Ethan's."],[1779,1970,"I've never even touched Sarah."],[1970,2144,"How the hell is this possible?"],[2454,2587,"Relax Sarah."],[2587,2804,"You've planned this perfectly."],[2804,2900,"No need to panic."],[4150,4229,"That cleaning maid,"],[4229,4374,"she reminds me of Nicole."],[4775,4929,"Everything reminds me of Nicole."],[4995,5194,"Maybe I just miss her too much."],[5575,5816,"Maybe, I just miss my baby so badly"],[5816,5920,"that I'm starting to believe"],[5920,6116,"in things that could never happen."]],"50":[[287,404,"Mr. Wilson,"],[404,491,"the stealth drone you developed"],[491,581,"won another tech award!"],[823,958,"Another tech award, huh?"],[1054,1125,"You know, this was Nicole"],[1125,1251,"and I used to dream."],[1251,1408,"Without her here, it means nothing."],[1600,1679,"Mr. Wilson,"],[1745,1852,"I know you've been down lately,"],[1852,1904,"so..."],[1954,2056,"I ran another background check"],[2056,2187,"on Nicole Brown."],[2345,2482,"And... what did you find?"],[2550,2630,"First of all,"],[2729,2886,"she's not legally married."],[2954,3020,"That Liam guy,"],[3020,3135,"I think he's just a friend."],[3279,3491,"Nicole, why would you lie to me?"],[3491,3579,"What is it that you're hiding"],[3579,3665,"from me?"],[3829,3983,"You go find out everything,"],[3983,4058,"all right?"],[4058,4152,"I want to know everything"],[4152,4241,"that's happened with Nicole"],[4241,4325,"the past seven years."],[4325,4409,"Got it?"],[4409,4508,"Yes, sir. I'm on it."]],"51":[[221,350,"Mr. Wilson."],[396,525,"Nicole, I'm losing my mind"],[525,588,"without you."],[588,729,"Let me go."],[804,871,"Please let me go."],[871,950,"Have some respect."],[950,1026,"I'm a married woman."],[1026,1134,"No, you're not."],[1317,1514,"You're single."],[1618,1697,"You did a background"],[1697,1818,"check on me."],[1851,1918,"If I hadn't,"],[1918,2006,"I never would have known"],[2006,2147,"how much suffering"],[2147,2298,"you've gone through."],[2406,2602,"Someone told you not to be with me,"],[2602,2736,"and you just did it."],[2882,2982,"I had a choice."],[2982,3065,"It's been seven years,"],[3065,3190,"and maybe"],[3249,3411,"staying away is the best ending"],[3411,3474,"for the both of us."]],"52":[[45,183,"Before I got my memory back,"],[183,283,"every time I saw you,"],[283,412,"I knew there was something special"],[412,542,"between us."],[579,675,"Every time that I saw"],[675,917,"that you were hurt, it hurt me too."],[975,1017,"Nicole,"],[1017,1084,"loving you"],[1084,1263,"is the whole reason that I'm alive."],[1317,1426,"You and I were meant to be"],[1426,1522,"together."],[1522,1659,"You can try and"],[1659,1764,"pretend to be married"],[1764,1901,"and make every other excuse"],[1901,2002,"in the world not to be with you."],[2002,2093,"But eventually I’m going to"],[2093,2256,"find my way into your heart."],[2385,2577,"Nicole, I'm going to fight for you."],[2577,2736,"I'm going to fight for us."],[2890,3082,"Our hearts already know each other."],[3219,3436,"And the only ending to this is with me."],[3578,3657,"It's the best ending."],[3657,3816,"It's the only ending."],[3870,3924,"So stop"],[3924,4066,"sacrificing your feelings"],[4066,4279,"and think about yourself for once."],[4733,4925,"But I've been to prison."],[4946,5063,"You were wronged."],[5063,5213,"I'll clear your name."],[5259,5413,"I don't know."],[5472,5676,"I mean us being together..."],[5676,5834,"It means a lot of people could"],[5834,5910,"get hurt."],[5947,6085,"And I'll protect them."],[6218,6339,"Nicole, I'll protect you."],[6339,6427,"I'll protect your grandma."],[6427,6610,"I'll protect everyone that you love."],[6710,6840,"No, the..."],[6877,6994,"the person that I'm worried about"],[6994,7219,"hurting is Lila."],[7561,7724,"Lila's already given me her answer."]],"53":[[216,412,"Lila loves you, Nicole."],[412,471,"You're the mom"],[471,567,"she's been dreaming"],[567,792,"and longing her entire life."],[1105,1217,"Nicole, how about we give this"],[1217,1334,"another chance?"],[2173,2364,"Nicole, will you marry me"],[2364,2431,"again?"],[4938,5050,"Sarah let it go."],[5050,5217,"You can't force love."],[5217,5451,"Ethan and Nicole are meant to be."],[5451,5751,"Don't make a fool of yourself."],[5989,6110,"Ethan suspects me, fine."],[6110,6210,"But my own mother telling me"],[6210,6297,"to give up?"],[6423,6523,"Idiots!"],[6556,6644,"All of them."],[7474,7603,"How dare they!"],[7711,7845,"Nicole you bitch!"],[7907,8124,"You think you can steal my man?"],[8550,8616,"No..."],[8679,8796,"this isn't over."],[8796,8950,"I can still turn this around."],[8950,9059,"Ms. Miller,"],[9142,9275,"do you have a plan?"],[9830,9914,"Push her."],[10047,10114,"What?"],[10189,10418,"Miss Miller, that's your own daughter!"],[10418,10497,"Do it."],[10593,10764,"That height won't kill her."]],"54":[[421,462,"This feels"],[462,621,"like a dream."],[1313,1443,"Ethan, it's Lila."],[1443,1584,"Come to the hospital!"],[1584,1639,"Now!"],[1639,1751,"We got to go."],[2206,2364,"What happened, did she faint?"],[2364,2464,"She fell down the stairs,"],[2464,2540,"but the doctor said"],[2540,2673,"she'll wake up soon."],[2965,3073,"Nicole, I know"],[3073,3211,"Ethan got his memories back,"],[3211,3332,"and he'll choose you"],[3332,3474,"without hesitation."],[3474,3641,"I just want you to know that."],[3678,3924,"I've decided to take a step back."],[4237,4308,"Sometimes"],[4308,4433,"you got to take a step back"],[4433,4579,"to move forward."],[4579,4675,"I'll break them"],[4675,4892,"if it's the last thing I do."],[4942,5142,"Lila's always liked you."],[5142,5359,"Please, take good care of her."],[5422,5551,"She'll be so happy to see you"],[5551,5668,"when she wakes up."],[5805,6072,"Ethan, Jackson called about"],[6072,6260,"some issue with the company."],[6297,6477,"You should get back to him ASAP."],[7899,8058,"Lila I'm here now."],[8087,8216,"You just focus on getting better,"],[8216,8304,"okay?"],[9663,9801,"Once this is done,"],[9801,9951,"there's no chance for you and Ethan"],[9951,10051,"anymore."]],"55":[[2089,2243,"Sarah?"],[2243,2452,"What are you up to this time?"],[2452,2656,"It's not about me."],[2656,2823,"It's about you."],[2823,2965,"Murderer!"],[2982,3136,"Murderer?"],[3153,3278,"Yes."],[3278,3445,"You killed my Lila."],[3445,3616,"No, no I didn't."],[3616,3749,"I didn't, I swear."],[3749,3928,"Your fingerprints are on the syringe."],[3928,4058,"Good luck explaining that."],[4099,4225,"Once everyone thinks you killed"],[4225,4354,"that little bastard,"],[4354,4525,"you'll be right back in jail."],[4525,4642,"I have a million ways to"],[4642,4792,"destroy you!"],[5096,5176,"Lila's not breathing!"]],"56":[[33,162,"Lila's not breathing."],[179,300,"You killed her."],[471,554,"I disabled all the"],[554,638,"surveillance cameras"],[638,834,"in this hospital long ago."],[834,1063,"Save your sob story for the jury."],[1063,1363,"But you'll always be a filthy murderer."],[1426,1626,"You're insane."],[1626,1755,"Useless slut!"],[1755,1868,"You think you could take Ethan"],[1868,1981,"from me?"],[1981,2085,"Well, I'm going to marry him,"],[2085,2185,"and I'll give him three,"],[2185,2339,"maybe five kids."],[2339,2481,"You are a monster."],[2481,2690,"Lila was six!"],[2690,2790,"Your own daughter."],[2790,2919,"How could you?"],[3048,3349,"You have no idea what's coming next."],[3365,3478,"If that bitch finds out"],[3478,3699,"it was her own daughter who died,"],[3699,3937,"she'll be devastated."],[3949,4070,"What?"],[4104,4300,"What are you talking about?"],[4362,4596,"What if I told you the one who died"],[4596,4842,"isn't my real daughter?"],[4842,4984,"It was yours!"]],"57":[[0,129,"Listen closely, bitch."],[129,262,"That little bastard is the baby"],[262,471,"you gave birth to all those years ago."],[588,754,"What?"],[871,1051,"Lila's my daughter..."],[1051,1172,"That's right."],[1172,1413,"I paid the doctor off."],[1705,2006,"You made me believe"],[2110,2344,"that my own baby was dead."],[2352,2573,"Are you nuts?"],[2573,2806,"More like genius."],[2806,2973,"While you suffered in prison,"],[2973,3178,"I brought your baby home to Ethan."],[3178,3424,"God, it was so fun."],[3424,3595,"You plotted all of this?"],[3595,3737,"I had no choice."],[3737,3837,"I grew up with Ethan,"],[3837,3970,"and I even went to college with him."],[3970,4087,"And he only looked at you,"],[4087,4245,"a stupid nobody!"],[4245,4546,"I'm rich like him, he should be with me!"],[4704,4842,"The thugs at the hotel?"],[4900,5038,"Henry tried to kill you?"],[5038,5201,"Lila's..."],[5201,5296,"accident?"],[5409,5463,"All me."],[5463,5572,"You're a demon."],[5659,5830,"I had your daughter call me mommy"],[5830,5947,"for six years."],[6093,6218,"And then I killed her"],[6218,6352,"and pinned it on you."],[6352,6481,"I win, and you're"],[6481,6719,"nothing but a sad, pathetic, loser."],[6961,7048,"I'm going to call Ethan"],[7048,7173,"so I can watch him"],[7173,7307,"drag you back to prison."],[7957,8066,"Ethan didn't leave?"]],"58":[[4,83,"I hope you don't mind,"],[83,354,"we stole your idea of hidden camera."],[629,788,"How is this possible?"],[942,1172,"The I.V. isn't connected, dummy."],[1184,1326,"You set me up."],[1326,1447,"You tricked me to confessing"],[1447,1647,"just now, didn't you, bitch!"],[1647,1743,"Get her out of here!"],[1743,1851,"Take her to the cops!"],[1910,2022,"Make sure they don't go easy"],[2022,2072,"on her."],[2306,2565,"You didn't win a damn thing, Nicole."],[2610,2777,"I'm the Miller heiress."],[2777,2940,"My mom will get me out of this."],[3090,3190,"Let me go!"]],"59":[[66,233,"Lila my baby."],[625,784,"Lila, baby,"],[846,921,"daddy has something"],[921,1042,"to tell you."],[1071,1184,"I already know."],[1184,1463,"I figured it out while I was sleeping."],[1526,1710,"You understood all of that?"],[1710,1893,"Yeah, I'm six, daddy."],[1893,2022,"Not dumb."],[2022,2164,"I was switched at birth."],[2164,2406,"Nicole is my real mommy."],[2515,2569,"Daddy,"],[2569,2786,"can I call her mommy now?"],[2786,2998,"Of course you can sweetheart."],[2998,3086,"Mommy! Mommy!"],[3086,3207,"Mommy!"],[3966,4170,"Here comes daddy!"]],"60":[[375,538,"Mom, what took you so long!"],[538,604,"Do you have any idea"],[604,734,"what I've been through?"],[734,871,"Get me out now!"],[930,1017,"No."],[1059,1222,"No?"],[1284,1422,"How could you do that?"],[1422,1659,"How could you turn so cold?"],[1659,1885,"Bribing doctors, switching babies,"],[1885,2177,"stealing Lila then trying to kill her?"],[2177,2448,"You are ruining your life."],[2448,2573,"And I've had enough of letting"],[2573,2761,"you get away with it over and"],[2761,2923,"over again."],[2957,3078,"Ethan and Nicole"],[3078,3240,"are going to get married"],[3240,3357,"just as they should have"],[3357,3474,"seven years ago."],[3474,3720,"And you, my daughter."],[3720,3999,"I am handing you over entirely"],[3999,4295,"to the court and the jury."],[4295,4491,"This time, it's time for you"],[4491,4683,"to pay the consequences."],[4683,4796,"No!"],[4796,4979,"Ethan's going to marry me!"],[4979,5125,"I'm Sarah Miller,"],[5125,5342,"I'm the heiress of this family!"]],"61":[[16,183,"Remember college?"],[183,433,"We used to fly our drones over there."],[592,746,"Hey, you remember when we used"],[746,963,"to make out over there?"],[1063,1309,"There were some pretty good times."],[1659,1693,"You know,"],[1693,1789,"these are some pretty darn"],[1789,1860,"good times, too."],[1860,2047,"You know?"],[2177,2369,"I love you, Nicole."],[2431,2515,"I love you, and I love"],[2515,2698,"our little girl."],[3361,3503,"I hope there's a little bit more room"],[3503,3753,"in that big heart of yours."],[4404,4617,"My god Nicole, are you serious?"],[4846,5013,"Oh my God."],[5121,5276,"My God."],[5342,5522,"I swear I won't miss a moment"],[5522,5822,"with you this time."],[6731,6981,"Ew, get a room."],[7261,7361,"Your mommy and daddy are"],[7361,7507,"very happy."],[7507,7645,"You want to celebrate with us?"],[7645,7791,"Only if you fly with me."],[7878,7974,"Deal."],[7974,8108,"Sounds like a challenge."],[8108,8254,"That sounds like a challange to me."],[8683,8929,"There were some pretty good times."],[9884,10135,"I love you Nicole."],[10135,10289,"I love you, and I love our little girl."]]}